UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'The first person to walk on the moon, Neil Armstrong, famously said, "That''s one small step for man, one giant leap for mankind." However, recordings of Armstrong''s transmission show that he actually said, "That''s one small step for *a* man, one giant leap for mankind."  What explains the discrepancy between Armstrong''s spoken words and the transcript of his transmission?',
